title: POPPY. IS. HAPPENING.
body: Guyz, poppy's files have been removed from the PBE. Guys. The time has come.

replies.body: Poppy and Taric reworks expected by the end of the year and early next year respectively
Yes we all knew that, BUT, HER FILES HAVE BEEN REMOVED FROM THE PBE
And, if you look at the latest PBE update, she's just had her rework added.
